text: Irmina Mrózek Gliszczyńska (born 9 February 1992) is a Polish competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Poland Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470 Category:470 class world champions Category:World champions in sailing for Poland Category:People from Chojnice
